division 245 1 these appeals by the applicant taxpayer in respect of the 2003 and 2004 tax years concern the application of the forgiveness of commercial debts provisions contained in div 245 of sch 2c of the income tax assessment act 1936 (cth).
2 broadly speaking, div 245 applies where there is forgiveness of a commercial debt .
